CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 14, 1963, pg. 12 reads: " 11th Year - Bob French, Pittsburgh representative, and Frank Cepits, district manager for Seagram Distillers Company display their Xmas packages and invite you to try Seagram's 7 Crown, V.O. and Gin for the holiday pleasure"
TitMainTitle: Regional sales manager Frank Cepits and sales representative Robert "Bob" P. French Jr., holding box of three bottles of Seagram products, posed in interior with bold block print patterned curtain
